{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemeswitchcomponenttokensprovider"]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of switch"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"switch \/ toggle"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"code":"OUDSSwitch","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"code":"AllSwitchComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"code":"SwitchComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"switch \/ toggle"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Switch"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of colors (from "},{"code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"spaces (from "},{"code":"AllSpacesSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":") ,  dimensions ("},{"code":"AllDimensionSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"sizes ("},{"code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"), borders ("},{"code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":") and opacities ("},{"code":"AllOpacitiySemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllSwitchComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent06SwitchB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/TokensProvider"]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"metadata":{"externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B34ThemeSwitchComponentTokensProviderC","symbolKind":"class","title":"OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider"}],"roleHeading":"Class"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"overview","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview"},{"code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for switch component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomSwitchComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the switch component tokens you want.","","        override var colorCursor: MultipleColorSemanticToken { colors.repositoryPositiveMedium }","","        override var spacePaddingInlineUnselected: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.fixed2xsmall }","","        override var size: SizeSemanticToken { sizes.iconWithLabelLargeSizeXl }","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomSwitchComponentTokensProvider: SwitchComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement maybe hundreds of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to use semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then, you can give this "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomSwitchComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" to your own theme implementation:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(switch: CustomSwitchComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"or to an already existing theme for example:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    OrangeTheme(switch: CustomSwitchComponentTokensProvider())"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeColorSemanticTokensProvider for colors","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeDimensionSemanticTokensProvider for dimensions","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider for spaces","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeOpacitySemanticTokensProvider for opacities","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeBorderSemanticTokensProvider for borders","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider for sizes","    let switchComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own dimension, color, border, space and opacities semantic tokens providers (or only some)","    let switchComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider(","                                                sizes: CustomSizesSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                borders: CustomBorderSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                colors: CustomColorSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                spaces: CustomSpaceSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                opacities: CustomOpacitySemanticTokensProvider()","                                                dimensions: CustomDimensionSemanticTokensProvider())"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.9.0","type":"text"}]}],"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"Since"}]}],"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"title":"Initializers","anchor":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider\/init(sizes:borders:colors:spaces:opacities:dimensions:)"]},{"generated":true,"title":"Instance Properties","anchor":"Instance-Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider\/borders","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThe